| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4872 — Mass File Rename (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 519e22bb-bb96-530d-bf9a-adbdcfac75ef"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
